race.comment: EIRE OF FORTUNE (10) goes on top. She ran well fresh at Colac at just her second career start, beaten under a length there in a 0-66. She should improve off that and with even luck from the inside gate she'll be very hard to hold out. TREASUREFLIGHT (9) resumes off a long spell. He's only won 1/10 to date but has run some solid races in better company. Respecting. THE PRINTER (7) Hit the line strongly first-up at Wangaratta and should relish the rise in trip second-up. Laid the foundations for a strong campaign last start and he can build on that here. SECOND FIX (12) struggled last time at Morphettville but prior form can see him in the finish.
